    "Name": "Decurion APC",
    "Details": "An offshoot of the Decurion Cavalry Tank, the Decurion APC was created to provide transport and battlefield support for the MHAF Infantry Contuberniums. Powered by the same 125-rated ICE as the standard Decurion, the project engineers opted to remove the Large Laser. The freed weight was used to add an extra half ton of armor protection and a 5 ton infantry bay. A pair of Medium Lasers were added and the Rocket Launcher 15's retained.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Biome Restrictions: This unit can not deploy in Lunar or Martian biomes due to using an ICE.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 hexes / 240/360 meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Armor\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       170     25\n<b>Left</b>         135     25\n<b>Right</b>       135     25\n<b>Rear</b>        120     25\n<b>Turret</b>      170     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      730    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color>\n\n<color=#ffcc00> Can carry 1 Battle Armor Squads.</color>",
